short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: A homework extension designed to ease homework sites

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Task Tackler is a collection of extensions designed to ease the use of multiple homework platforms including Sparx, Seneca, Bedrock, and more by providing a range of features.

V4 is now out!

Task Tackler now has a dashboard for settings, data and bug reporting at https://www.task-tackler.com/dashboard

Sparx:
- Built in answer revealer (ai powered)
- Automatic bookwork saving and filling
- Built in calculator (desmos)

Seneca:
- Auto fills answers
